                    <span>This book is wonderful.  Finally a writer who starts a book with a introduction that is a page turner from start to finish.  Madiosn thought she lived the perfect life until slowly she has to face the reality of her life as her "so perfcet life" turns into a whirlwind of events that she either has to accept or hide from and struggle to survive all the challengs put in her way.  I am waiting her next book, Someone To Love Me.</span>
                  
